text: Novosimskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Iglino, 4 km from Kaltovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Novosimskoye
